Class ObservableGameState

  • java.lang.Object
    • core.ObservableGameState

  • public class ObservableGameState
extends java.lang.Object
    This class acts as a buffer between GameState and Players. It allows players to see information but not change it. Because this is a buffer class, see GameStates JavaDoc for descriptions of methods
    Author:
    William Elliman
